descriptionHtml:
Just to know, these textures are not for your character but for the npcs. It's an UNP Fix

As the title says, textures replacements if you are using the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?]DIMONIZED UNP female body[/url] or similar derivates. There is a small harmless esp file to fix a texture path for the afflicted female hand. There are a bit of [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Female Textures Renewal[/url] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion[/url] textures mix'n merged with the vanilla ones. Done just to try out [url=http://www.maxon.net/products/bodypaint-3d/why-this-package.html]Bodypaint 3D[/url].  Screenshot with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36067/?]Vividian ENB[/url]. Colors and brightness are the same of the vanilla files. No fancy screenshots
author: NevenBridge
